products:
Our most popular wood shutter is manufactured by a local company 
that uses the highest high quality wood and paints, so your shutters
look better and last longer at a fraction of the price.

More important - we are able to custom design and install your 
shutters quickly. No long wait period.

Have a look at our samples and see the quality difference.

Our most popular vinyl shutter is made by Canada's 
premier manufacturers of windows - your vinyl is made of
the same pure un-recycled vinyl resin that will not change 
colour or warp.

CHECK OUT OUR WEBSITE FOR MORE PRODUCT DETAILS.

profile:
Manufacturing quality wooden Plantation and California Shutters

Experienced and Reliable
With over 10 years in the shutter manufacturing business, we at Ontario Shutters Direct are confident in providing excellent quality shutters at a very competitive price.

We Care About the Details
Whether it's the colour, or type of design, or which hinges to use, we at Ontario Shutters Direct will get specific on how you like your shutters to look in your home.

Customer Satisfaction Guaranteed
We believe our work is not complete until you are 100% satisfied and happy with our product. You are covered for service even after our installers have left your home.
